Package gw.plugin.contact.findduplicates.querybuilder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCompositeFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    An extension of the {@link AbstractFieldExpression} class offering methods to work with child expressions. The collectTableNames and isValid methods delegate to the children. before calling abstractdoOperate which has to be overriden by subclasses.
    AbstractFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    A base implementation for the {@link FieldExpression} methods. The operate method will check isValid before calling abstractdoOperate which has to be overriden by subclasses.
    AndCompositeFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    A composite expression encapsulating child expressions with an "And" operator.
    CompanyQueryBuilder<T extends ABCompany>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABCompany} queries.
    CompositeExpression<T extends ABContact>
    A composite expression containing logic for handling child expressions.
    ContactQueryBuilder<T extends ABContact,U extends ContactQueryBuilder<T,U>>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABContact} queries.
    ContactQueryBuilderBase<T extends ABContact,U extends ContactQueryBuilderBase<T,U>>
    A {@link Query} builder creating queries for a given {@link ABContact}.
    EqualFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    Represents an "Equals" expression comparing a database value against a given value.
    FieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    Represents an expression on a given field. Valid expressions are for instance: {@link EqualFieldExpression}, {@link InFieldExpression}, {@link StartsWithFieldExpression}.
    InFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    Represents an "In" expression comparing a database value against an Array of values.
    OrCompositeFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    A composite expression encapsulating child expressions with an "And" operator.
    PersonQueryBuilder<T extends ABPerson>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABPerson} queries.
    PersonQueryBuilderBase<T extends ABPerson,U extends PersonQueryBuilderBase<T,U>>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABPerson} queries.
    PlaceQueryBuilder<T extends ABPlace>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABPlace} queries.
    StartsWithFieldExpression<T extends ABContact>
    Represents a "Starts With" expression comparing a database value to subsets of a given value.
    UserContactQueryBuilder<T extends ABUserContact>
    A {@link Query} builder offering methods for building {@link ABUserContact} queries.
